value.title: Opinion: Like Donald Trump in ’16, Larry Elder May Benefit from All the Criticism
value.excerpt: Elder may be, as his critics say, unfit to be governor. However, like Trump, he probably loves the attention because his enemies are making him more friends.

value.title: Trump says Kabul airport explosion wouldn’t have happened if he was president
value.excerpt: Donald Trump hammered Biden over the suicide bombings outside Kabul’s airport, claiming that “it would not have happened if I was your president.”

value.title: Psaki dismisses calls for Biden to resign: 'Not a day for politics'
value.excerpt: White House Press Secretary Jen Psaki dismissed calls for President Joe Biden to resign in the wake of a terrorist attack in Kabul, Afghanistan that killed 13 U.S. service members, saying that there’s no room for politics in the discussion of the tragedy.

value.title: Biden doesn't deny report of US handing over names of Americans to Taliban: 'There may have been'
value.excerpt: President Biden did not deny a report circulating Thursday that officials in his administration had provided names of Americans in Afghanistan to the Taliban in order to help usher them safely to the airport.

value.title: Biden condemns 'vicious' ISIS attacks in Kabul: 'We will hunt you down and make you pay'
value.excerpt: President Biden pledged to take action against ISIS-K militants and complete evacuation operations on Thursday in his first public remarks since a pair of deadly suicide bombings targeted U.S. forces and evacuees at Kabul’s airport in Afghanistan.

value.title: Ezra Klein’s Best Defense of Joe Biden: ‘It Could Be Worse!’
value.excerpt: Looking at a bad situation that could, and should, have been avoided and defending it solely on the basis that it could have been worse is not analysis. It’s spin.

value.title: Biden ally claims Trump greater 'threat' to US than al Qaeda
